                    <div class="bz-nc-body">
                        <div style="font-size:38px;margin-bottom:12px;">🔌</div>
                        <h4>Not Connected to biziShip.ai</h4>
                        <p>
                            You need to connect your BiziShip.ai account before getting freight quotes or booking shipments.
                        </p>
                        <p style="color:#888;font-size:13px;margin-top:8px;">
                            Click <strong>Connect Now</strong> — enter your email, receive a one-time PIN, and you'll be ready to go.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <footer class="bz-nc-footer">
                    <button string="Cancel" class="btn-bz-cancel" special="cancel" data-hotkey="z"/>
